  <section class="story-section">
    <div class="story-inner">
      <p>Signs.inc started with a simple frustration. Walking down Main Street in any town, you see storefronts with dignified, well-built signs that have stood for years, and right next to them, peeling vinyl banners and cheap plastic boxes that look tired the day they go up.</p>

      <p>Businesses deserved better. Our founders, a second-generation metal fabricator and a designer who grew up in a family hardware store, set out to bring back the kind of sign work that lasts. The kind a shop owner is proud to point at when their grandkids visit.</p>

      <div class="story-pullquote">
        Every sign we make goes up on someone's life work. That deserves the same care a watchmaker gives to a movement, or a luthier gives to a guitar.
        <small>&mdash; Founding Principle, Signs.inc</small>
      </div>

      <div style="margin:38px 0;border-radius:14px;overflow:hidden;box-shadow:0 18px 42px rgba(0,0,0,.12)">
        <img src="https://i.ibb.co/zhVSVypQ/SKb-Yc.jpg" alt="Skilled hands wiring LED modules into custom aluminum channel letter sign at signs.inc factory – signs.inc" style="width:100%;height:auto;display:block" loading="lazy">
      </div>

      <p>Today, we manufacture for hundreds of businesses every year, from family-owned restaurants in small towns to franchise locations in major metros. There is no middleman, no broker markup and no game of telephone between you and the people actually building your sign.</p>

      <p>We use UL-listed components on every illuminated job. We weather-seal every weld. We test every LED before it ships. We back every sign with a five-year warranty because we know what we built and we know it will hold.</p>

      <div style="margin:38px 0;border-radius:14px;overflow:hidden;box-shadow:0 18px 42px rgba(0,0,0,.12)">
        <img src="https://i.ibb.co/SwYmFwgr/Q3CVw.jpg" alt="Completed custom channel letter sign sets on factory storage rack ready for shipping – signs.inc" style="width:100%;height:auto;display:block" loading="lazy">
      </div>

      <p>And we work with businesses of every size on terms that respect the way they run their books. No giant deposits, no surprise fees, no fine-print games. Just quality craftsmanship at a fair price, delivered when we said we would.</p>

      <p>If your business has earned its place on Main Street, your sign should reflect that. That is what we build here. Every day, every sign.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

